OL,5, Female police officers are posing as   
OL,6, runners as part of a crackdown on      
OL,7, strangers catcalling women out         
OL,8, exercising in Bradford.                
OL,10,FThose found to be harassing women could
OL,11,Fbe fined up to #1,000.                 
OL,13,FThe measures come after a survey by    
OL,14,FRunner's World magazine which found 60%
OL,15,Fof female runners had experienced      
OL,16,Fharassment, largely from men in cars.  
OL,18,FSupt Beth Pagnillo said women should be
OL,19,Fable to "run freely without being      
OL,20,Fconcerned".                            
